      • getOffset

        public java.lang.String getOffset()
        Description copied from interface: InlineQuery
        The offset for this query, this can be used to enable pagination when the user scrolls to the end of the current list of results. When this happens, the API will provide an identical InlineQuery object with an offset that was set in the previous inline query response. This makes it possible to return more results that are different from the first set of results
        Specified by:
